---
title: Comforting Chorizo & Veggie Traybake with Silverbeet & Mayo
description: Mild chorizo adds instant charm to a trayful of veggies in this no-fuss recipe, imparting a lovely salty and smokey flavour. Along with the mild silverbeet, the sweetness from the pumpkin works to balance out the richness of the dish.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
